The '''Zyggurats''' were a terrorist group that operated on the fringes of the known [[Galaxy/Legends|galaxy]] during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] once saved [[Shug Ninx]] after the latter was found to be running [[ion trigger]]s for them.

